Our Hotel

   All rooms of the Hotel Basel were completely renovated in 2018 and now
   73 guest rooms shine in new splendour. Not least because of our
   location and our name, we are very close to the city of Basel. This is
   reflected in all areas of our hotel: in the rooms, in the materials
   used, in our restaurants, with our suppliers and partners. Come in and
   see for yourself!

   In addition, we have put together an interesting shopping offer for you
   with over 30 shops around the Hotel Basel.

   explore our rooms

Our restaurants

   Please take a seat in one of our restaurants – be it the Brasserie
   Steiger, the Sperber Bar or the Boulevard during the summer season -
   optimal service is our passion.

   Our kitchen team has exciting culinary suggestions in store for you!

    explore our restaurants

